      <title>noob chanter question about charming</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Enchanters&amp;message.id=6146#M6146</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;Had someone tell me that I had to do at least 5 hp's of damage to a mob if I'm using a charmed pet or if the charmed pet does all the damage I'll get greatly reduced exp.&amp;nbsp; Person suggested I get a clickie band or ring that could do this minimal damage mana free.&amp;nbsp; I'm only level 28 and have crappy gear and am wondering what kind of gear to look for.&amp;nbsp; Should I be seeking charisma maximizing stuff?&amp;nbsp; I've played pet class(necro) and have played a wizzie a little so don't really want to nuke and would rather try charming.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
